working in groups of no more than 4 you are required to use multimedia authoring software to design an interactive non linear digital noticeboard.

you can design a noticeboard in any of the following 7 areas: 1) Tourism 2) Business and Commerce 3) Technology (cryptocurrency) 4) Music and Fashion 5) Travel 6) Music 7)

6) Food and Cooking 7) Fintech

each group will present your noticeboard at the end of the term together with a 2 page MS Word soft copy report (format of report to be announced later)

